encyclopaedia.entry_sorting module¶

encyclopaedia.entry_sorting.push_locked_to_bottom(seq)[source]¶

Moves all the locked entries in a list of entries to the bottom of the list.

Parameters:seq – The sequence of EncEntry to sort.
Returns:Sorted version of the given sequence
Return type:list
